      <content>
        <section>
          <marginalnote>Bylaws under section 124 of the <actname>Motor Vehicle Act</actname> prescribed</marginalnote>
          <sectionnumber>1</sectionnumber>
          <sectiontext>Bylaws made under section 124 of the <actname>Motor Vehicle Act</actname> are a prescribed category of bylaw for the purposes of section 272 (1) (a) of the <actname>Local Government Act</actname>.</sectiontext>
          <hnote>[en. B.C. Reg. 190/97.]</hnote>
        </section>
        <section>
          <marginalnote>Bylaws under section 31 of the <actname>Islands Trust Act</actname></marginalnote>
          <sectionnumber>1.1</sectionnumber>
